                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-orange-500 mr-2 mt-1"></i>
                                    <span><strong>GPT AI 무제한</strong> (현재: 100건/일)</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-orange-500 mr-2 mt-1"></i>
                                    <span><strong>AI 발음 코치 무제한</strong> (현재: 100건/일)</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-orange-500 mr-2 mt-1"></i>
                                    <span><strong>전용 계정 매니저</strong> - 1:1 맞춤 지원</span>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-4">
                            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">구독 시작일</p>
                                <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800" id="subscriptionStartDate">-</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">다음 결제 예정일</p>
